original_title: Juice=Juice＆カントリー・ガールズ LIVE ～梁川奈々美 卒業スペシャル～
overview: Juice=Juice and Country Girls' joint 2019 live. The first live was held on February 14, 2019 at Zepp Namba. The second live was held on March 11, 2019 at Zepp Tokyo, titled Juice=Juice & Country Girls LIVE ~Yanagawa Nanami Sotsugyou Special~ where concurrent Juice=Juice and Country Girls member Yanagawa Nanami graduated from both groups and Hello! Project.
title: Juice=Juice & Country Girls LIVE ~Yanagawa Nanami Sotsugyou Special~
